(1151,'The Venture Company <illegible text> It would seem that the fools nearly wiped out their entire operation in trying to stabilize the mixture.\n\n<several pages appear to be torn out>\n\n',1152,1),
(1152,'What I have noticed is that the fallout is extremely lethal. Imagine if <illegible text> Hahaha! ',1153,1),
(1153,'Am I going mad? Today I severed the head of one of my most trusted patrollers in order to get a better look at their soul. As I peered down their severed breathing passage, it occurred to me: I had not eaten anything in days!\n',1154,1),
(1154,'Mathias Shaw has sent an errand boy to kill me. <illegible text>\n\nHe patrols outside now. Mindless, lifeless drone.\n\nHahahah!',1155,1),
(1155,'VanCleef...<illegible text>\n\nCalled me IN?? WHO DOES HE THINK HE IS?? I am Klaven Mortwake! I shall not be told what to do by an insect!\n\n<the rest of the pages in the book are missing>',0,1),
(1156,'Curgle, $B$BI have been eagerly awaiting your newest invention. I can\'t wait to begin using it to document my studies.$B$BPlease entrust it to my messenger.$B$B$BWith kindest regards,$B$BDaryn Lightwind',0,11723),
(1170,'Curgle, I have been eagerly awaiting your newest invention. I can\'t wait to begin using it to document my studies. Please entrust it to my messenger. With kindest regards, Daryn Lightwind ',0,1),
